definition.value: A chlorobenzoate that is the conjugate base of 4-chlorobenzoic acid.
A disaccharide consisting of D-glucono-1,5-lactone having a beta-D-glucosyl residue at the 4-position.
The steroid sulfate of taurolithocholic acid.
A 2-oxo monocarboxylic acid anion that is the conjugate base of 4-methyl-2-oxopentanoic acid.
